{"tid":2081061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"季炳強：「我會盡力將你地身份隱藏，你地可以為所欲為」","createTime":"2020-06-27T02:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T21:00:42.000Z","uid":230104,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"864e2f32a256adf9302bfd0aa7668ed440e27ea2","tid":2081061,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70ai4SK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70ai4SK.png&h=271fb60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民權監察成員沈偉男批評，警方去年11月「鬼祟」修改警例，於沒對外公佈下，容許警員處理示威時，僅以行動呼號作身份識別，此舉令警員匿名狀態下為所欲為，「做乜都冇後果，變相助長警暴！」沈指即使市民欲投訴警員，由於無法得悉對方身份，案件往往不了了之，令投訴機制名存實亡。港版國安法實施在即，惟政府遲遲未公佈具體細節，沈擔心警方將動輒以國安為由鎮壓市民，令警暴進一步升級。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200627&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20945233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200627%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20945233&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=206a436b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200627%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20945233&h=78ee8546\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200627&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20945233</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一步就係大貪特貪，呢個係定律<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBAbFrt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBAbFrt.jpg&h=97cceaf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d54c2bf8357a431d94e7f83fafa13b5af28a01f7","tid":2081061,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"只會越來越腐敗"},{"pid":"7206a477528591fb60df208c8349a7900e27ac98","tid":2081061,"uid":281328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"「警暴」「濫權」呢啲字太斯文了<br />\n唔係咁啱形容皇軍"},{"pid":"96890485965049547ede873d0f403bd974659989","tid":2081061,"uid":